down. It's not the power.

105
00:11:55,147 --> 00:11:57,482
Maybe there was an earthquake.

106
00:11:57,483 --> 00:11:59,028
Here?

107
00:12:17,169 --> 00:12:18,771
Jesus Christ.

108
00:12:20,606 --> 00:12:21,878
What?

109
00:12:26,345 --> 00:12:27,753
