That was the Power
of Rap, 102.2 F.M.

112
00:12:36,222 --> 00:12:38,302
Radio stations are down.

113
00:12:40,326 --> 00:12:42,360
I can't believe it.

114
00:12:42,361 --> 00:12:43,599
What?

115
00:12:45,464 --> 00:12:48,101
It finally happens and I'm
stuck in a fucking elevator...

116
00:12:51,837 --> 00:12:53,712
with you.

117
00:12:55,141 --> 00:12:56,379
You.

118
00:13:09,321 --> 00:13:10,593
Captain.

119
00:13:12,424 --> 00:13:15,693
- What's the update?
- There's gonna be a short delay

120
00:13:15,694 --> 00:13:17,362
before we can get you out, ma'am.

121
00:13:17,363 --> 00:13:20,298
Why? What's going on? Why are
the phones down, the radios?

122
00:13:20,299 --> 00:13:23,134
I don't have that
information right now.

123
00:13:23,135 --> 00:13:25,146
As soon as I do, I will
pass it on, ma'am.

124
00:13:26,372 --> 00:13:27,705
You need to remain calm.

125
00:13:27,706 --> 00:13:29,707
We're doing everything we can.

126
00:13:29,708 --> 00:13:31,442
This is unacceptable.
Who is in charge?

127
00:13:31,443 --> 00:13:32,944
We'll contact you shortly.

128
00:13:32,945 --> 00:13:34,679
Blau...

129
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:36,418
shit.

130
00:14:26,232 --> 00:14:28,573
All I could think about was Lauren.

131
00:14:30,469 --> 00:14:36,018
Her dad died before she was
even born and I'm all she has.

132
00:14:39,545 --> 00:14:42,247
I think the only reason I
survived being tortured

133
00:14:42,248 --> 00:14:44,682
was to get back to her.

134
00:14:44,683 --> 00:14:47,696
And then I got back to her and
then I endangered her life.

135
00:14:49,722 --> 00:14:52,490
There was just a night where
I ended up waking up,

136
00:14:52,491 --> 00:14:55,693
standing in the middle...
of the street

137
00:14:55,694 --> 00:14:59,139
with cars passing, and
holding her and screaming.

138
00:15:00,065 --> 00:15:02,567
And I woke up while I was
holding her and screaming

139
00:15:02,568 --> 00:15:05,148
and I didn't know how I got there.

140
00:15:20,219 --> 00:15:21,627
You hear that?

141
00:15:23,022 --> 00:15:25,256
You mean the game?

142
00:15:25,257 --> 00:15:27,564
Turn that off.

143
00:15:29,328 --> 00:15:31,772
Hey, I said turn it off.

144
00:15:35,901 --> 00:15:37,878
I said, fucking turn it off.

145
